## Chip

**Classes**: `tl-chip`
**Sizes**: `tl-chip--sm` (24px), `tl-chip--lg` (32px)
**States**: `tl-chip--selected`
**Modifiers**: `tl-chip--prefix`, `tl-chip--suffix`

```html
<button class="tl-chip tl-chip--lg">Default</button>
<button class="tl-chip tl-chip--lg tl-chip--selected">Selected</button>
<button class="tl-chip tl-chip--sm" disabled>Disabled</button>
```

