## Tabs

### Inline Tabs

```html
<div class="tl-inline-tabs" role="tablist">
  <button
    class="tl-inline-tabs__tab tl-inline-tabs__tab--selected"
    role="tab"
    aria-selected="true"
  >
    Tab 1
  </button>
  <button class="tl-inline-tabs__tab" role="tab" aria-selected="false">
    Tab 2
  </button>
  <button
    class="tl-inline-tabs__tab tl-inline-tabs__tab--disabled"
    role="tab"
    aria-disabled="true"
  >
    Disabled
  </button>
</div>
```

### Folder Tabs

```html
<div class="tl-folder-tabs" role="tablist">
  <button
    class="tl-folder-tabs__tab tl-folder-tabs__tab--selected"
    role="tab"
    aria-selected="true"
  >
    Active
  </button>
  <button class="tl-folder-tabs__tab" role="tab" aria-selected="false">
    Another
  </button>
</div>
```

### Navigation Tabs

```html
<nav class="tl-navigation-tabs" role="tablist">
  <a
    class="tl-navigation-tabs__tab tl-navigation-tabs__tab--selected"
    href="/overview"
    role="tab"
    aria-selected="true"
    >Overview</a
  >
  <a class="tl-navigation-tabs__tab" href="/details" role="tab">Details</a>
</nav>
```

