## Link

**Classes**: `tl-link`
**Modifiers**: `tl-link--underline`, `tl-link--standalone`, `tl-link--disabled`

```html
<a href="/page" class="tl-link tl-link--underline">
  Learn more
  <span class="tl-link__icon"
    ><span class="tl-icon tl-icon--arrow_right"></span
  ></span>
</a>

<!-- Standalone link (inherits detail-02 typography) -->
<a href="/page" class="tl-link tl-link--standalone tl-link--underline"
  >Standalone Link</a
>

<!-- Disabled link -->
<span class="tl-link tl-link--disabled">Disabled link</span>
```

